    <div class="content">
      <p>The general idea of the <em>Linux Quiz</em> is to use quiz questions as starting points for discussions where participants with less experience can learn new things from the particpants with more experience, who can share their knowledge, hopefully making the quiz fun for people of all experience levels.</p>
<p><a href="Linux_Quiz:Questions" title="wikilink">Questions</a></p>
<h2 id="history">History</h2>
<ol>
