<li>Call for questions: <a href="http://lists.tlug.jp/ML/1404/msg00100.html" class="uri">http://lists.tlug.jp/ML/1404/msg00100.html</a></li>
<li>Follow-up: <a href="http://lists.tlug.jp/ML/1405/msg00041.html" class="uri">http://lists.tlug.jp/ML/1405/msg00041.html</a></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="suggestions">Suggestions</h2>
<ul>
<li>Make all participants write down their answer before sharing possible answers. Perhaps participants can use <code>man</code> all they want but avoid using the Internet to search or answers.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Turn the quiz into a contest, where more than one person “races” to complete tasks. This type of quiz would probably be pretty exciting.</li>
</ul>
